"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"女学生A","body":"就是这个！主唱简直太厉害了~！\nLAYER小姐不管是唱歌还是弹贝斯，都非常帅气！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"女学生B","body":"我懂，真的很帅气……！\n只要她的声音一出来，就算她只是在画面边缘\n我的目光也会不自觉地追随她呢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"女学生A","body":"没错没错！我把视频循环看了好几遍哦~\n还有，DJ和鼓手也很帅气，\n吉他手和键盘手超级可爱！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"（又是『鼓手也』吗……）","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"angry01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event288-02-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"女学生B","body":"不过，大家都非常投入，\n感觉很有激情呢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"女学生A","body":"对~\n她们是不是和JRF的运营方有什么过节啊","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChan